abstract: This script was designed to replace two Javascript-based
  chiming clocks that deliver time information from two different
  time systems. In addition to Westminster-style quarterly chimes,
  between sundown and sunrise it also sounds chimes that allow the
  current night watch (according to the proportional decimal time
  system in use c. 7â€“2c BC in the geographical region now known as
  China) to be sonically identified. Care is taken to avoid the two
  kinds of chimes from running together.

